(12, 'How To Create An Effective Explainer Video For Your Company', '<p id=\"isPasted\" style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Nowadays, videos are essential to success. There has been a desire to emphasize video content above all else. If you want to create a brand that succeeds above all expectations, you should be aware of the best methods for promoting your brand.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Moreover, the potential for brand awareness is the key to the brand&#39;s success. Today, in this blog post, we will be discussing the importance of explainer videos. So, an explainer video is an instructional video. Consumers watch and comprehend explainer videos 96% better than any other form, according to a study.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">The following information will help you create a successful explainer video for your brand. So, without further ado, let&rsquo;s start.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-size:33px;font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Why Do Explainer Videos Exist?</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">If you want to communicate what you have to offer or what you want to sell to your target audience, you can do so with the aid of an explanation video. It is the best way to effectively promote the brand message. An explainer video provides the following benefits to the user or the brand: So, using an explainer video for your brand is one of the smartest moves one could make. Here we go!</span></p><ul style=\"list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:26px;\"><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Higher engagement</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">High Google ranking</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Boosted sales conversions</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Sharing content becomes simple.</span></li></ul><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-size:33px;font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">How Can I Create A Tutorial Video?</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">The steps listed above must be followed in order to create an explainer video:</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-size:32px;font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Choose A Specialty</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Making sure that your explainer video will be as relevant to your audience as possible requires some preliminary research. as it would help you produce the best explainer video. You must be knowledgeable about the subject if you want the greatest final results, which include more sales and higher brand awareness. So, use all viable research techniques, including Google Analytics, to gather insightful data about the issue.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-size:32px;font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Select The Type And Style</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">So, there are virtually no restrictions on the types and styles that can be used in an explainer video. These are some concepts you may employ for your explainer video; all you need to do is do some study or seek advice from a professional explainer video services provider to determine which would best suit your needs and preferences.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">So let&#39;s first examine the list of types:</span></p><ul style=\"list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:26px;\"><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">explanation animation</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Whiteboard explainer video</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">live-action explanation video</span></li></ul><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Let&#39;s examine the video styles now:</span></p><ul style=\"list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:26px;\"><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">informal videos</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Educational videos</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">instructional movies</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Sales video</span></li></ul><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-size:32px;font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Script Writing</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">So, in the explainer video, there is a framework, which is the screenplay. Without a strong script, even the amazing visual components won&#39;t work. So, if you&#39;re paying a production team to construct the explainer video for your brand, creating the screenplay yourself makes sense because no one understands your customers better than you do, including their pain points and preferences.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-size:35px;font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">Conclusion</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;color:#252525;background:white;\">This brings us to the end of the story! You would probably be helping yourself by creating the best explainer video for your brand if you followed these guidelines. If you are unable to do it, don&#39;t be afraid to seek professional assistance.</span></p>', 'Nowadays, videos are essential to success. There has been a desire to emphasize video content above all else. If you want to create a brand that succeeds above all expectations, you should be aware of the best methods for promoting your brand.', 'animated logo', 'public/images/posts/1699097308explainer-video.jpg', 'animated logo', 'Admin', 'public/images/posts/1699097308person.png', 'public/images/posts/1671994715How To Create An Effective Explainer Video For Your Company.jpg', 'How To Create An Effective Explainer Video For Your Company', 'Nowadays, videos are essential to success. There has been a desire to emphasize video content above all else. If you want to create a brand that succeeds above all expectations, you should be aware of the best methods for promoting your brand.', 'How-To-Create-An-Effective-Explainer-Video-For-Your-Company', NULL, '2022-12-25 13:58:36', '2022-12-25 13:58:36', 'branding'),
(15, 'What Are the Seven Steps in Animated Video Creation?', '<p id=\"isPasted\" style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>If you want to convey more information in a shorter amount of time, you should look for something that is efficient, clear, and thorough. Such tools in today&#39;s quick-paced environment are simply videos themselves. As we have all seen, a variety of industries employ animated videos to advertise their goods and services. It is because the audience gets reached quickly. It&#39;s in style!</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>However, if you don&#39;t adhere to a specific framework, creating one is difficult. Making animated videos involves adhering to a few fundamental rules. These include writing for voice-over, animation, storyboarding, and scripts. Let&#39;s now dig deeper and be a little more specific.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-size:33px;font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>Writing A Brief</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>A brief is, in essence, your plan. It is a message that you formulate for your audience. A strong brief should contain all of these topics, as well as the kind of artwork you use. Don&#39;t forget about any particulars, like color, length, and tone. You cannot begin production without a brief.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-size:33px;font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>Conceptual Consideration</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>Do you come up with any ideas while producing an animation video? It is the area of the process that receives the least attention. As a result, these organizations give concepts a lot of weight.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>When you&#39;re working on an animation video, think like a creator rather than a videographer. Most of the time, individuals merely pay attention to the video, and they lack the ability to add notions. as it is the most valuable element in the creation of an animation video. Work arduously on the ideas if you want to create something special that captivates the audience and helps people remember your message for a lifetime.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-size:33px;font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>Write Scripts</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>Your video&#39;s script acts as its structure. A compelling story may make up for even subpar audio and visuals. All of us have seen films with similar elements: a large budget, fantastic effects, monsters, and a forgettable narrative. That all lies in the script. But without a strong storyline, even a million-dollar explainer video that looks amazing could fail to sell anything.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-size:33px;font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>Designing</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>When everything is decided, design and/or character art are created. This displays a static but exact replica of the look of the video.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-size:33px;font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>Animation</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>After all the previous processes are finished, the animation starts. A frame is a section of a visual composition where the video is seen. Thankfully, the procedure has now become easier with the use of excellent tools. There is still a lot of work to be done to make sure everything looks good and works smoothly.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-size:33px;font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>Sound And Voice Over</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>The voice-over and sound design are added at this level, which is the final step. There are many companies that offer top-notch services for producing animation videos if you are not skilled at doing so or do not have the necessary equipment.</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-size:35px;font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>Briefly Stated</span></p><p style=\'margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\'><span style=\'font-family:\"Roboto Light\";color:#252525;\'>So you can now see the various steps involved in creating a polished and appealing animated video. We have written this blog to help you get acquainted with some helpful information that might be able to assist you in the future, whether you are a learner or a professional agency.</span></p>', 'If you want to convey more information in a shorter amount of time, you should look for something that is efficient, clear, and thorough. Such tools in today\'s quick-paced environment are simply videos themselves.', 'animated videos', 'public/images/posts/1699097308animated-videos.jpg', 'animated videos', 'Admin', 'public/images/posts/1699097308person.png', 'public/images/posts/1672068503pexels-kyle-loftus-3379934.jpg', 'What Are the Seven Steps in Animated Video Creation?', 'If you want to convey more information in a shorter amount of time, you should look for something that is efficient, clear, and thorough. Such tools in today\'s quick-paced environment are simply videos themselves.', 'what-are-the-seven-steps-in-animated-video-creation', NULL, '2022-12-26 10:28:23', '2022-12-26 10:28:23', 'animated videos'),
